Where are you?

45
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:22,580
Call me back immediately.

46
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,620
The streets in Paris are chaotic.

47
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,140
Don't wander alone.

48
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:48,230
Hello?

49
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:50,630
Alright.

50
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,080
Okay.

51
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,810
I'm heading to the office right away.

52
