(China Customs)
Ladies and gentlemen, good morning.

54
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:17,840
The flight to New York

55
00:10:17,850 --> 00:10:20,010
(From Zhuang Guodong: What happened?)
now begins the check-in process.

56
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:21,340
(Call me when you see this.)
Please take

57
00:10:21,340 --> 00:10:22,810
(Don't wander alone.)
your luggage and tickets

58
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,340
to Counter 14
according to the instructions

59
00:10:24,350 --> 00:10:26,620
(To Zhuang Guodong: Landed in Beijing safely.)
to complete your check-in.

60
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,190
Thank you.

61
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:37,490
(Pick up the phone. Why did you leave suddenly
without saying anything?)

62
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:39,020
(To Huang Yimei: Do you know
how worried I was?)

63
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:40,820
(From Zhuang Guodong: What's wrong?
Why is your phone off?)

64
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,500
(Rose, what happened?
Call me back. Are you angry again?)

65
00:10:42,580 --> 00:10:45,620
(To Zhuang Guodong:
The company needs me urgently.)

66
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,440
Ms. Jiang.

67
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,410
- Hello, Ms. Jiang.
- Hello, Ms. Jiang.

68
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:41,290
Ms. Jiang, these contracts
need your signature.

69
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:43,870
Leave them here.

70
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,380
Is there anything else I can do?

71
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:53,380
Nothing, you can go back first.

72
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:55,960
Wait.

73
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,410
Could you get me a coffee?

74
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,340
(Su)
Paris is beautiful,

75
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,460
but I don't belong here.

76
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,070
The body's back,

77
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:37,340
but when will the spirit be back?

78
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:39,750
Su,

79
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:42,860
have you ever had a moment

80
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:46,140
where suddenly

81
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,460
everything

82
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:52,650
became clear?

83
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:57,750
An epiphany.

84
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:00,390
Epiphanies happen in an instant,

85
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:02,440
but before they happen,

86
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:04,860
one goes through a long period

87
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:07,150
of struggle, conflict,

88
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,010
and self-doubt.

89
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,220
Once it happens,

90
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,500
things become different.

91
00:13:34,660 --> 00:13:36,180
(User information)

92
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:46,300
(Eric: Meeting a friend from Germany today.
Won't video call for now.)

93
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:55,860
(Alright.)

94
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,770
Hello, Ms. Jiang.

95
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,360
(Room 6)
The situation has stabilized,

96
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:21,440
but pregnancy at this age

97
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:23,140
still carries some risks.

98
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,280
She should stay in the hospital
for a few days

99
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,500
for comprehensive checks.

100
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,460
- Okay.
- What's your relationship with her?

101
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:31,390
She's my boss.

102
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,980
If surgery is needed later,

103
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,840
we'll need a family member's signature.

104
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,000
Can you contact them?

105
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:37,840
Room 6.

106
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,220
- Over there.
- Thank you.

107
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,960
How did it go?

108
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:49,030
Did she have a miscarriage?

109
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:59,100
Seems not.

110
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,170
You knew?

111
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,040
Just a few days ago,

112
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:04,360
I saw her throwing up in the bathroom.

113
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:06,010
She probably realized it herself
at that moment.

114
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,390
Isn't she single?

115
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:09,890
Who told you she was single?

116
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,720
Right. She just didn't mention it.

117
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,190
I'll ask Amy to find

118
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:18,430
the emergency contact for employees

119
00:15:18,430 --> 00:15:19,590
and get her husband's number.

120
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:20,430
Don't.

121
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:22,600
She's already filed for divorce.

122
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,080
Let her decide

123
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,260
whether to tell him or not.

124
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,170
What kind of person is her husband?

125
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,440
His surname is Gu.

126
00:15:30,150 --> 00:15:32,340
Tina met him when she was studying
in New York.

127
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:34,080
He helped her

128
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,460
get into the art circle.

129
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:38,050
Why don't they live together?

130
00:15:38,670 --> 00:15:40,190
Mr. Gu's company is in Hong Kong, China

131
00:15:40,190 --> 00:15:41,960
and Tina can't let go of Beijing.

132
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,770
They've been separated for a long time.

133
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:45,620
Just two months ago,

134
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,320
didn't Tina go to Hong Kong, China?

135
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,670
She went to talk to Mr. Gu about divorce.

136
00:15:49,670 --> 00:15:52,050
Probably got pregnant then.

137
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,580
Are they still divorcing?

138
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,140
Better start the procedures.

139
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,650
Why haven't you left yet?

140
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:22,160
I didn't misjudge you.

141
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:23,790
You understand me too well.

142
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:25,630
I was just thinking about this.

143
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:26,690
Does the doctor allow this?

144
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:28,870
I'm not having the surgery tomorrow.

145
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:29,710
Come on.

146
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:35,040
Why is there just one cup?

147
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:35,880
Where's yours?

148
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,400
How many times have you stolen my drink?

149
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:40,480
Do you think I don't know?

150
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,320
Stop pretending.

151
00:16:44,270 --> 00:16:45,110
Hurry up.

152
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,690
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

153
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:09,350
Ms. Jiang,

154
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:11,490
is the child Mr. Gu's?

155
00:17:15,350 --> 00:17:16,400
Of course.

156
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,450
Who else's could it be?

157
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:20,340
Good for you, Ms. Jiang.

158
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,110
Getting more vigorous as you age.

159
00:17:22,110 --> 00:17:23,210
Age? What do you mean?

160
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:24,920
Mr. Gu.

161
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,210
Isn't he almost sixty?

162
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,540
Yes.

163
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:31,250
Come on.

164
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:34,140
How did this old ox

165
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,250
sow the seeds?

166
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:42,140
Ms. Jiang, I have a question.

167
00:17:42,510 --> 00:17:45,170
How did pregnancy and divorce

168
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:48,380
occur simultaneously?

169
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:00,210
Xueqiong,

170
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,450
why did you suddenly come to Hong Kong, China?

171
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:15,310
You could have let me know before coming.

172
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,450
I could have picked you up.

173
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:19,780
Come, sit.

174
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:24,820
Are you hungry?

175
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:27,650
I can have something prepared.

176
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:29,280
No need.

177
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,970
Come, have some tea.

178
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,380
You should

179
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,490
sign it.

180
00:18:58,110 --> 00:19:00,100
The lawyer has already told me about it.

181
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,250
I roughly know the contents.

182
00:19:06,510 --> 00:19:07,410
My dear,

183
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,580
is this all you want?

184
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:13,020
There are still your shares
in the company.

185
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:15,170
You've earned them

186
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:17,820
over the years.

187
00:19:24,510 --> 00:19:25,450
It's been eight years.

188
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:29,780
Eight long years.

189
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:32,380
So many beautiful memories.

190
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:40,300
Do you really want nothing?

191
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:41,920
Don't you regret it?

192
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:43,340
You've given me a lot already.

193
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:45,890
From you,

194
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:48,140
I gained insight,

195
00:19:49,270 --> 00:19:50,110
resources,

196
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:53,480
and love.

197
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:56,820
Love?

198
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:03,910
Love.

199
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:11,890
Though we still love each other,

200
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:13,860
we can't accompany each other anymore.

201
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,380
Then let each other be free.

202
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:24,100
Leaving a lover and giving up a child.

203
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:26,890
Won't you regret it in the future?

204
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,250
Since we've come to this point today,

205
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:37,300
let me say a few more words to you.

206
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:54,170
Gu and I

207
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:56,450
have actually been separated
for many years.

208
00:20:57,350 --> 00:20:58,630
One in Hong Kong, China,

209
00:20:58,630 --> 00:20:59,620
and the other in Beijing.

210
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:03,340
He refused to move to Beijing for me,

211
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:06,630
and I couldn't go to Hong Kong, China for him,

212
00:21:06,630 --> 00:21:08,210
giving up everything in Beijing.

213
00:21:10,790 --> 00:21:12,540
We've both studied art.

214
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,240
You tell me.

215
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:17,070
Which expresses the self more,

216
00:21:17,070 --> 00:21:18,490
assigned work or free creation?

217
00:21:19,030 --> 00:21:20,490
Of course, it's free creation.

218
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:24,830
Marriage and having children, for me,

219
00:21:24,830 --> 00:21:26,170
are like assigned work.

220
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:29,170
I love him very much,

221
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:33,100
but I don't want to be just Mrs. Gu.

222
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:36,140
I want to be myself.

223
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:41,860
So, I choose free creation.

224
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:28,450
Excuse me, whom are you looking for?

225
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:31,760
Xueqiong.

226
00:22:38,590 --> 00:22:39,540
Let him in.

227
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:01,950
Sorry.

228
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:03,590
Could you give us more time?

229
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:05,720
Just tell me if there's anything
we need to prepare.

230
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,750
Okay, the surgery is in half an hour.

231
00:23:07,750 --> 00:23:09,580
All jewelry must be removed.

232
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:10,960
She hasn't eaten or drunk anything, right?

233
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:11,800
No.

234
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:13,000
Okay. Half an hour.

235
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:13,840
Thank you.

236
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:46,690
Thank you.

237
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,540
Take care of her.

238
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:53,860
Remind her to eat on time.

239
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:56,650
Don't let her drink alcohol anymore.

240
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,620
No alcohol in the hospital.

241
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,820
Not everyone is lucky enough

242
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:35,620
to encounter true love

243
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,490
in their lifetime.

244
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,620
But I still have many things to do

245
00:24:43,070 --> 00:24:44,100
and many paths to walk.

246
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:46,560
These

247
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,170
are just as important as love.

248
00:24:57,590 --> 00:24:58,890
Didn't you ask me before

249
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:01,820
if I would regret it?

250
00:25:02,030 --> 00:25:03,250
You won't regret it.

251
00:25:04,510 --> 00:25:06,310
You have the determination
to see it through to the end,

252
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:08,540
and the courage to accept loss.

253
00:25:16,060 --> 00:25:18,700
(Divorce Agreement)

254
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:19,950
Send this

255
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,210
to my lawyer.

256
00:25:31,300 --> 00:25:33,820
(Divorce Agreement)

257
00:26:01,890 --> 00:26:03,680
(Video chat)
It's been a while since we last video chatted.

258
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:04,560
How have you been lately?

259
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,340
Still the same.

260
00:26:07,270 --> 00:26:08,890
Tina was hospitalized recently,

261
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:12,140
and she didn't assign me
any important tasks.

262
00:26:12,350 --> 00:26:13,730
Now that there's no overtime,

263
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:15,210
I'm still getting used to it.

264
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:18,480
Not sure if there will be another chance

265
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:19,780
to work as a curator.

266
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:21,890
Do you miss me?

267
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:23,520
Yes.

268
00:26:26,550 --> 00:26:29,620
They said I had the highest score
in this training.

269
00:26:30,510 --> 00:26:32,100
But there's nothing to be proud of.

270
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:34,680
I've learned all this before.

271
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,650
In another month,

272
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:38,210
this management training
will be over for good.

273
00:26:38,590 --> 00:26:40,300
Naomi has already informed me

274
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:42,880
that the position of Marketing Manager

275
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,310
is almost certain.

276
00:26:44,310 --> 00:26:45,690
How's that? Good news, right?

277
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:48,930
Congratulations.

278
00:26:49,550 --> 00:26:50,890
Once this job settles down,

279
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:53,150
after being here for five years,

280
00:26:53,150 --> 00:26:54,540
I can apply for permanent residency.

281
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:06,440
Oh, my mom recently introduced me

282
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:08,200
to a Belgian collector

283
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,300
